OL,3,CNo evidence of 'two-tier policing' in
OL,4,Csummer riots response, MPs say
OL,6,FPolice forces responded in an
OL,7,F"entirely appropriate" manner, despite
OL,8,Faccusations that those involved in
OL,9,Fsummer riots were policed more
OL,10,Fstrongly than previous protesters, MPs
OL,11,Fhave said.
OL,13,FA new report from the Home Affairs
OL,14,FCommittee has looked into the police
OL,15,Fresponse to the disorder that followed
OL,16,Fthe murder of three girls at a Taylor
OL,17,FSwift-themed dance class in Southport
OL,18,Fon July 29 last year.
