OL,3,CNo evidence of 'two-tier policing' in
OL,4,Csummer riots response, MPs say
OL,6,F"It was disgraceful to see the police
OL,7,Fofficers who bore the brunt of this
OL,8,Fviolence being undermined by baseless
OL,9,Fclaims of 'two-tier policing'."
OL,11,FDuring the riots, mosques, community
OL,12,Fcentres and libraries were attacked,
OL,13,Fand hotels housing asylum seekers were
OL,14,Falso targeted.
OL,16,FCommittee chairwoman Dame Karen
OL,17,FBradley added: "Organised disorder is
OL,18,Frightly met with a robust response;
OL,19,Fany implied equivalence with planned
OL,20,Fnon-violent protests is simply wrong."
