OL,3,CNo evidence of 'two-tier policing' in
OL,4,Csummer riots response, MPs say
OL,6,FBy January 22 this year, 1,804 arrests
OL,7,Fhad been made, and there were 1,072
OL,8,Fcharges from the disorder, with the
OL,9,Fmajority for serious public order
OL,10,Foffences, the report said.
OL,12,FIn total, 246 events of protests,
OL,13,Fcounter-protests and incidents of
OL,14,Fdisorder took place, including 88 seen
OL,15,Fas "significant" with many resulting
OL,16,Fin disorder, it added.
