OL,3,CNo evidence of 'two-tier policing' in
OL,4,Csummer riots response, MPs say
OL,6,FIn the worst violence seen since the
OL,7,F2011 riots, MPs urged the government
OL,8,Fto release funding to forces to cover
OL,9,Fthe costs from the disorder, which was
OL,10,Festimated to total more than #28
OL,11,Fmillion by the National Police Chiefs'
OL,12,FCouncil.
OL,14,FThey also called for the government to
OL,15,Ffocus on a strategy for retaining
OL,16,Fpolice officers, alongside
OL,17,Frecruitment, after staff during the
OL,18,Friots worked for long hours with many
OL,19,Fsuffering injury and trauma.
