OL,3,CNo evidence of 'two-tier policing' in
OL,4,Csummer riots response, MPs say
OL,6,FSome 44,438 public order police
OL,7,Fofficer shifts were worked to cover
OL,8,Fthe national response to the disorder
OL,9,Fbetween August 1 and 18, while 302
OL,10,Fofficers were injured, including up to
OL,11,F69 who were taken to hospital.
OL,13,FThe report said: "Police forces did
OL,14,Ftheir best to ameliorate the impact on
OL,15,Fofficers but it is clear that the
OL,16,Fdisorder has had a detrimental effect
OL,17,Fat a time when many officers were
OL,18,Falready struggling with heavy
OL,19,Fworkloads, fatigue and stress."
