OL,3,CNo evidence of 'two-tier policing' in
OL,4,Csummer riots response, MPs say
OL,6,FMPs also found shortfalls in national
OL,7,Fpolicing structures that hindered the
OL,8,Fresponse to the disorder, and meant
OL,9,Fforces were not always able to access
OL,10,Fsupport they needed.
OL,12,FThe parliamentary committee agreed
OL,13,Fwith findings from a watchdog that
OL,14,Fpolice forces should have better
OL,15,Fanticipated the risk of disorder in
OL,16,Fgeneral, and that it should not have
OL,17,Fbeen taken for granted that planned
OL,18,Fprotests following the Southport
OL,19,Fdisorder would remain peaceful.
