OL,3,CNo evidence of 'two-tier policing' in
OL,4,Csummer riots response, MPs say
OL,6,FHis Majesty's Inspectorate of
OL,7,FConstabulary and Fire and Rescue
OL,8,FServices (HMICFRS) had said that a
OL,9,Fnumber of events in 2023 and 2024 were
OL,10,Findicators of potential future
OL,11,Fdisorder, but this had not been
OL,12,Freflected in police intelligence
OL,13,Fassessments.
OL,15,FIt also found there were gaps in
OL,16,Fintelligence linked to social media
OL,17,Fand the dark web.
OL,19,FMPs also recommended a boosted ability
OL,20,Ffor police to monitor and respond to
OL,21,Fsocial media at a national level.
