OL,6,FIt was also highlighted that the
OL,7,Fcriminal justice system has failed to
OL,8,Fkeep pace with the social media age,
OL,9,Fwhich created an information vacuum
OL,10,Fthat "allowed disinformation to
OL,11,Fflourish" in the wake of the Southport
OL,12,Fmurders.
OL,14,FThe report recognised the belief that
OL,15,Fspeculation and misinformation that
OL,16,Fthe suspect was an asylum seeker was a
OL,17,Fdriver of disorder.
